Think you can blast through 5 levels with only one life? Prove your balloon-bustin’ skillz in this Blasting event and earn some rewards while you’re at it!
15 new map levels coming soon in Theme Park!
And as usual, MORE CHALLENGES: More pigs, more balloons, more BLASTING!

BLAST OFF with the new update!
- Get ready for Mighty League Tournaments!
- 15 Blasterific new map levels coming soon
- Plus bugs blasted (as usual)

Limited-time events, sales, and spooky surprises come to Angry Birds Blast for Halloween!
– 2 NEW MIghty League events – Play new levels and earn killer rewards in the spooky cabin in the woods.
– A Halloweeny Daily Quest – Play the fearsome daily quest to earn some sweet goodies!
– Halloween everything! Skulls! Bats! Pumpkins! Everywhere you look, things are looking spookier.
BALLOONS INFLATED: New levels to BLAST!

BLAST away the fall blues!
– The new MIGHTY LEAGUE season is upon us
– Special BLACK FRIDAY & CYBER MONDAY offers
– Blast your way trough 5 LEVELS with only ONE LIFE
– Join other players for cool prizes in the TEAM RACE
– Plus 15 blasterific new map levels coming soon...

'TIS THE SEASON TO GET BLASTY!
– Mighty League: New levels & snowy rewards in the Winter Wonderland
– Treasure Hunt: 5 levels in Santa’s workshop - but only one life!
– Daily Quest: Play the frosty daily quest to earn some toasty prizes!
– Puzzle Hunt: Complete that xmassy puzzle!
– Offers & Sales: Grab great deals on coin and booster bundles

'TIS THE SEASON TO GET BLASTY!
– NEW EVENT: Your very own Christmas tree to decorate!
– Xmassy EVENTS: Daily Quest, Team Race, Treasure Hunt and more all with a seasonal twist!
– Happy Blastday: Angry Birds Blast turns 1, so lookout for a little gift from the flock!
– NEW LEVELS: Get Blasting, yo!
– iPhone X support: yay!

'TIS THE SEASON TO GET BLASTY!
– NEW EVENT: Your very own Christmas tree to decorate!
– Xmassy EVENTS: Daily Quest, Team Race, Treasure Hunt and more all with a seasonal twist!
– Happy Blastday: Angry Birds Blast turns 1, so lookout for a little gift from the flock!
– New Year EVENT: Mighty League brings in the new year!
– NEW LEVELS: Get Blasting, yo!

New year, new update!
– More Events: Treasure Hunt, Team Race and more!
– More Levels: Blast 'em!
– New Puzzle: Find the pieces!
Plus the usual liberal application of Bug Spray.

BALLOONS INFLATED: New levels to BLAST
More balloons inflated, blocks built, sandwiches filled and glass... err... blown. Update today and keep blasting!
MORE BLASTILICIOUS NEW LEVELS! Plus more bugs blasted, and other small tweaks too detailed to list here (yet important enough to mention). Go get blasting!

"New update out now!
– NEW PHOTO ALBUM! Complete goals every month to fill your photo album and win rewards!
– UNLIMITED LIVES! For everyone, every Monday.
– MIGHTY LEAGUE! Climb the league. Win prizes. Every weekend.
– NEW LEVELS! 15 every week, check the end of the map!

Be sure to update to the latest version for the newest features, events and levels! New update versions arrive every 3 weeks."

Love is all around us, and with new levels, lovely decorations, and special sales, there’s no denying it – Valentine’s Day is here!
– Two new Valentines Events: Treasure Hunt and Crown Rush!
– NEW levels!
– Charming Valentine’s decor.
– Valentine’s Day offers in the shop!

Add a spring to your step with our NEW UPDATE!
– EASTER! Enjoy the Super tasty Mighty League and Egg Hunt events!
– THRONE RUSH! 5 levels in 1 life - our mini game gets a makeover!
– NEW LEVELS! New main map levels now added every MONDAY!
– And of course a few more bugs blasted...

Blast into a springtime update with new levels and weekly events!
– NEW levels every Monday! We're passing the 1000 levels mark. Who's gonna get there first?
– Themed Throne Rush chosen by our community! Coming soon…
– Mighty League! Climb the league. Win prizes. Play every weekend.

"Keep blasting through spring with tons of fun new stuff!
– NEW PHOTO ALBUM! Complete goals every month to fill your photo album and win rewards!
– UNLIMITED LIVES! For everyone, every Monday.
– COMMUNITY VOTED EVENT! You choose what we'll play, check our Facebook page...
– MIGHTY LEAGUE! Climb the league. Win prizes. Plus, is that wedding bells I hear?
– NEW LEVELS! Every Monday of course!"

Summer up with Blast update! We are introducing a new division in Mighty League: Master!

– NEW DIVISION IN MIGHTY LEAGUE! Reach for the Master division!
– PHOTO ALBUM! Complete goals every month to fill your photo album and win rewards!
– UNLIMITED LIVES! For everyone, every Monday.
– NEW LEVELS! Every Wednesday!

Get your BLAST on with a new update!

What's new:

– PIGGY BANK! Beat levels, fill the Piggy Bank, get discounts!
– NEW DIVISION IN MIGHTY LEAGUE! Reach for the Master division!
– PHOTO ALBUM! Complete goals every month to fill your photo album and win rewards!
– UNLIMITED LIVES! For everyone, every Monday.
– NEW LEVELS! Every Wednesday!

Be sure to update to the latest version for the newest features, events and levels!
What's new:
– Challenge yourself with the new Hard Mode in Treasure Hunt!
– Piggy Bank! Beat levels, fill the Piggy Bank, get discounts!
– New division in Mighty League: Master.
– Unlimited Lives! For everyone, every Monday.
– New levels every Wednesday!

Rule the Blast Kingdom with the help of a special booster!
What's new:
– Catch the Throne Rush special booster: 30 minutes of unlimited +3 moves!
– Piggy Bank! Beat levels, fill the Piggy Bank, get discounts!
– New division in Mighty League: Master.
Stay tuned for more new features, events and levels!

We’re preparing the launch pad for some out of this world events starting on October 2nd. Get ready to blast off!
-October 2nd: Mars Rover Treasure Hunt!
-October 5th: Space Launch Mighty League!
-October 9th: Moon Landing Throne Rush!
More bugs blasted, animations optimized and balloons inflated. Update today and get blasting!

Get ready for a fright fest of spooky events as Angry Birds Blast gets a Halloween and Day of the Dead makeover!

October 19th: Halloween Mighty League part 1
October 22nd to 29th: Pumpkin Pig Poppin' Daily Quest time-mode
October 23rd: Dracula's Throne Rush
October 26th: Halloween Mighty League part 2
October 30th: Day of the Dead Treasure Hunt
October 31st: Booster Bonanza! (Exclusive new event!)
November 2nd: Day of the Dead Mighty League

– Visit the Blast community page for news, contests and more! https://www.facebook.com/angrybirdsblast/
